<a name="gloves_of_the_gatecaller"></a>
<font color="#FFFFFF" face="Arial">
<strong>Gloves of the Gatecaller - AC 3</strong>
<font size=-1></font><BR>
Slot: <a href="/armour/hands.shtml">Hands</a><BR>
Weight: 5.5 - All Races<BR>
Classes: <a href="/enchanter/armour/hands.shtml">ENC</a>, <a href="/magician/armour/hands.shtml">MAG</a>, <a href="/necromancer/armour/hands.shtml">NEC</a>, <a href="/wizard/armour/hands.shtml">WIZ</a><BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) (No Drop) (Lore) <BR>
</font>

</td></tr>
