<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>These gloves are cool just for the look(look like black chainmail).  They are very heavy, but look awesome with almost any robe(especially gossamer, FBR, or yellow/blue/red training robes).  I wear them in favor of raw silk, bear-hide, or even dusty bloodstained if I'm wearing a robe they go with.</font></td></tr></table>
