<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Ok there is a question/rumor that by wearing these gloves, when killed, one does not loose as much exp as another that isn't wearing the gloves. Well I find that very interesting indeed. That would more then make up for the weight of the gloves. I will test this rumor and make a post as to its validity. The test will be conducted during by two level 46 characters. Im sure everyone is aware of the difference of exp loss w/ regard to level 31,36,41, and 46.<BR>
<BR>
On a closing note, despite its great weight, still not a bad item for level 1 newbie with no exp on the bar to obtain. </font></td></tr></table>
